b"Naomi and Jason walked into our Germantown, Wisconsin, store engaged and walked out married. The couple picked up a package at the store's @UPS Access Point location :love_letter: opened it then and there and signed on a dotted line. Their excitement was clear as they told our Team Members that their signatures on the document made it official \xe2\x80\x94they were married :party_popper::bride_with_veil::man_in_tuxedo:
:two_hearts:
Naomi and Jason planned to get married on March 20, 2020, at the Milwaukee County Courthouse, but amid COVID-19 concerns the courthouse closed its doors. So, Naomi and Jason changed gears. A coworker got ordained to officiate the wedding and married the couple in the living room of their new home :house_with_garden:

Naomi shared her favorite photo from the day with us, which she described as, \xe2\x80\x9cJust pure happiness amongst all the craziness in the world right now!\xe2\x80\x9d :two_hearts::party_popper:Congratulations, Naomi and Jason!!"
